title: 1 nice bed 1 bath 1 den ( Daly City)
posting_body: ['1 nice bedroom with 1 den and 1 bath on the ground floor with a separate entrance.', 'A den is a small bonus room, which can be used as a small office.', 'Start to show on 8/6/22', 'Key highlights:', '- Separate entrance', '- 1 bedroom, 1 den, 1 bathroom with a refrigerator!', '- All utilities are paid by tenants with the arrangement.', '- Street parking only', '- Laundry access; No waterbed', '- No Pet, no drugs, no vape, no smoking of any kind, no parties, and no loud noise', '- No sub-leasing or short-term leasing.', 'No illegal activities.', 'Other highlights', '- Easy Access to freeway 280 in both north and south directions', '- Walking distance to bus stop 120', '- Close to Ranch 99, and Serramonte shopping mall, Target, Sprout supermarket, in-and-out, and much more', 'Showings:', 'By appointment only.', 'If interested, pls provide the following information:', '- Does anyone smoke?', '- Expected move-in date,', '- Any pets?', '-  # of people?', 'What do you guys do for a living?', 'How long have you been working there?', 'What’s the monthly estimated income?', '- Why are you moving?', 'Requirements:', 'Move-in cost: Rent: first month $1895+ Security deposit $1,895 =total move-in cost: $3,790 due at signing', 'Lease term: 1-year lease', 'A copy of the full credit report dated within 30 days', '- Latest 2 months of the pay stubs and bank statements', '- Reference from job and from previous landlords', '- Latest 2 months proof of rent payments']
